    <string name="about_highlights">- Discover trending content ideas\n- Generate video ideas from any topic\n- Write editable YouTube scripts\n- Create Shorts scripts quickly\n- Generate SEO titles, descriptions, and tags\n- Save and manage creator projects</string>
    <string name="about_built_for_title">Built For</string>
    <string name="about_built_for">YouTube creators, students, educators, tech creators, storytellers, and anyone who wants to create content faster with AI support.</string>
